%% POST /auth/login の処理シーケンス

sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant FB as Firebase Auth
    participant R as Route
    participant A as get_current_firebase_user
    participant FI as init_firebase
    participant S as UserService
    participant UR as UserRepository
    participant DB as Database

    Note over FE,FB: 1. Frontend側でFirebase認証
    FE->>FB: signInWithPopup / signInWithEmail
    FB-->>FE: Firebase ID Token

    Note over FE,DB: 2. Backend APIコール
    FE->>R: POST /auth/login with Bearer token

    R->>A: Depends get_current_firebase_user
    A->>FI: init_firebase()
    FI-->>A: firebase_admin App

    A->>FB: auth.verify_id_token
    FB-->>A: decoded claims

    alt Token Invalid
        A-->>R: HTTPException 401
        R-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    A-->>R: decoded dict

    R->>R: Validate LoginRequest

    R->>S: UserService db
    R->>S: get_or_create_user

    S->>UR: get_user_by_firebase_uid
    UR->>DB: SELECT users WHERE firebase_uid
    DB-->>UR: User or None
    UR-->>S: existing user or None

    alt User Exists
        S-->>R: existing_user, False
    else User Not Exists
        S->>S: Create new User model
        S->>UR: create_user
        UR->>DB: INSERT users
        DB-->>UR: User
        UR-->>S: new_user
        S-->>R: new_user, True
    end

    R->>R: UserResponse.model_validate
    R-->>FE: JSON Response 200 OK
